'''Grand Nord''', also known as '''Kamaib''' in an ancient [[Morse (Karlatt)|Morse]] dialect, was the [[Planet/Legends|planetary]] [[Capital/Legends|capital]] of [[Karlatt]]. Located on an isthmus between the planet's two continents, it was a metal jungle with an [[Imperial-class spaceport]] that boasted countless hotels, casinos aplenty, omnipresent surveillance [[Droid/Legends|droids]], and innumerable security cameras. The public was always kept tranquil by the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Empire]]. The city was known for the [[Park of Fumes]], a gigantic thermal establishment in open air. The city was home to the [[Planetary Council]]. Numerous worlds had ambassadors dwelling in Kamaib.

